_sText:
This is a map for my clan VNV. We have a zombie mod server and I though we could use some more maps so... I decided to make one! There is a ton of rooms and hiding spots all with props so you are able to make barricades. As far as I've seen, there is no cheap spots, I tried to even things out a bit by the number of entrances to certain rooms and how many props are in those rooms.

Don't forget to favorite this map and add me to your watchlist!
